item.description: Anyone up for dinner at Sakura tepanyaki grill. This will be a great time with great food from the grill to sushi for anyone who dares to try. The band that night is Pet Rock so get your legs warmed up for dancing or have a drink in the lounge after dinner. We will meet in the lounge at 7:30 for anyone wishing to join us before dinner...I will make reservations for 8:30 for dinner for those who wish to meet us then..
item.name: Sakura Tokyo
